title: LF - High Gold/Plat Rank Jungle Main (Clash & Flex)
body:
Need a High Gold/Plat player for our clash team who mains jungle. 

Things to look for:
A decent champ pool and be willing to play meta 
(We're fine with niche champs as long as you're consistent but it's not pref)
